      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "魏氏"
      ],
      "text": "这也是天命定数有修短，劝国母切莫要终日泪涟。为报恩来世里重亲慈范，千古人有哪个百岁同餐。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01005009_e00030",
      "play_id": "01005009",
      "scene_id": "01005009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "武姜"
      ],
      "text": "听儿言不觉得珠泪悲惨，纵然是鬼与魂娘也心甘。怎能够同聚首襟怀坦坦，随为娘在此地同把身安。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01005009_e00031",
      "play_id": "01005009",
      "scene_id": "01005009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "共叔段"
      ],
      "text": "儿在阴母在阳两厢隔断，母子们要相逢今生实难。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01005009_e00032",
      "play_id": "01005009",
      "scene_id": "01005009_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "反二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "魏氏"
      ],
      "text": "天将明儿要归不尽感叹，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01005009_e00033",
      "play_id": "01005009",
      "scene_id": "01005009_s02",
